The Illinois Network of Charter Schools (INCS) will host its 13th annual Teacher &amp; Administrator Job Fair on Saturday, April 7, 2018 at Perspectives/IIT Math &amp; Science Academy (3663 South Wabash Avenue, Chicago, IL 60653). Representatives from the state’s charter schools will be on hand to recruit hundreds of teachers, social workers, counselors, nurses, and other administrators - such as marketing managers, college coaches, and finance operators.  You can learn more about the FREE fair and upload your resume to the year-round resume bank at the following link: www.teacherjobfair.org.  

